oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Bill Long's Place, W. Depot Street, 1935
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Thompson Brothers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: 100-114 W. Depot Street, 209-211 N. Central Street. Ordered by R.W. Perrin. April 16, 1935. Bill Long's Place --Cigars, Tobaccos, Lunches. Coca-Cola sign. Signs in window ofr Foss-Schneider beer. Cars parked on street.
